title: Weekend Quilting Wonders
description: There isn't a more glorious way to spend a weekend than to spend it quilting! And now, that weekend can be better than ever because all 40 projects in this book can be started and finished in the same weekend. Projects range in size from small table runners to queen-size bed quilts. Many projects can be completed by a beginner and all can be completed in a weekend by someone with average quilting ability.
